sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server
    participant StripeAPI as Stripe API
    participant Checkout as Stripe Checkout

    Client->>Server: Send order information
    Server->>StripeAPI: Create Checkout Session
    StripeAPI-->>Server: Return Checkout Session
    Server->>Client: Redirect to Checkout URL
    Client->>Checkout: Open Checkout Session
    Checkout->>Checkout: Customer completes payment
    Checkout-->>Client: Redirect back to application
    StripeAPI-->>Server: Webhook (payment completed)
    Server->>Server: Handle fulfillment
